description:
Recently sold: $282,000. **Contact Mike Pahl 651-491-4905 (Text) or mike.pahl@evusa.com to schedule a showing!**

Welcome home to this nicely updated cape cod style home located just minutes away from the lakes, biking and walking trails.  This 1.5 story home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  As you walk in the front door you are greeted by dark hardwood floors, white trim and a large family room.  The kitchen is updated with stunning dark walnut cabinets, custom tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and granite counter-tops.  The large deck is located right off the kitchen and is perfect for entertaining. The large flat yard is newly seeded and is fenced in, perfect for pets.  

Located on the main level is two bedrooms and a nicely updated bathroom. As you make your way upstairs you will notice the custom wood beams in the upper bedroom and plenty of room makes this a spacious master suite.

The downstairs is comprised of a 4th bedroom, laundry room, living room, game area, and a 3/4 bathroom.  Perfect set-up to have friends and family over to hangout, and enjoy company. 

Many other updates include, carpet, washer/dryer all about 2 years old and the roof is about 5 years old.

Book a showing before it is gone, this one won't last long!!
